[30;1m2 | [0m[35m# Custom exceptions must NOT expose data including hostnames, pathnames, IP addresses, etc. (securit[0m
[30;1m3 | [0m[35mclass SshError(Exception):[0m
[30;1m4 | [0m[35m    """ Base class for all SSH error classes.[0m
